# Ashok AI Day Planner

A smart personal day planner with an AI chat assistant to schedule tasks, get reminders, and plan your perfect day. Manage your daily routines efficiently with conversational AI.

## Features

- Add, view, and manage daily routines.
- Chat with AI (`phi3`) to plan your day interactively.
- Automatic reminders and scheduling.
- Supports natural language input for task planning.

## Quick Start

1. Clone the Repository:

git clone <your-repo-url>
cd <project-folder>

2. Create and Activate a Virtual Environment:

python -m venv venv

# On Windows:

venv\Scripts\activate

# On macOS/Linux:

source venv/bin/activate

3. Install Dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt

4. Install and Run Ollama:

Download Ollama: https://ollama.com/download

#) Pull the Phi3 Model:

ollama pull phi3

#) Start the Ollama Server:

ollama run phi3

This will start the Ollama server on http://localhost:11434, which your Flask app will interact with.

5. Run the Flask Application:
   cd webapp
   python app.py

Your application should now be accessible at http://127.0.0.1:5000/.

# Later, replacing JSON for anydatabase is simple:

# Just create a SQLite database (routines.db).

# Replace load_routines() and save_routines() with SQL queries.
